{"tid":827434,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(濕疹)d手指，掌心開始出現圈圈","createTime":"2018-09-19T02:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T05:00:36.000Z","uid":6989,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2d35a10bd3bd2683565250fbef33f3ee9bc8bc","tid":827434,"uid":6989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:27:14.000Z","msg":"利申 輕微。本身係右腳出先，睇完醫生食左1星期藥（類固醇+抗敏），有改善。食完藥過左一星期，手掌開始有d位痕，左腳腳板長時間行路都好易痕。跟住去覆疹，今次食2星期藥，冇類固醇，正係抗敏感藥，止痕。有改善既，但見到d手指開始好似有鄺散？ 唔痕，正係乾。<br />\n<br />\n想問 我由得佢 定係要點做呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/102627_ad986c664eb951f7c58313d90cbf1c7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F102627_ad986c664eb951f7c58313d90cbf1c7e.png&h=f6a63348&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/102633_a8d9a831aa42c226f4548b320eef93d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F102633_a8d9a831aa42c226f4548b320eef93d5.png&h=413ff4aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6567f55f47d016075d179972c8a850f63de86b8b","tid":827434,"uid":6989,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0b0879f2a40e57966edb2f2ef3cfef446af428","tid":827434,"uid":201512,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"汗疹，平時做下運動出一身汗啦<br />\n利申:濕疹十二年，呢兩年做運動沒再發"},{"pid":"679205087e7da2eb77d4e8708fb79db4c6d9673a","tid":827434,"uid":201512,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T02:55:23.000Z","msg":"唔好再搽類固醇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" 